name: Erin Britton
description:
im adventurous, in any kinds. i like to travel, read books, and going to the beach or pool for a quick dip. i have a deep connection with tequila, a really really really deep connection. im not an alcoholic, don’t get me wrong, i just like tequila. but wine…it’s ok. i kind of consider myself as a nerd at the same time, if you’re into that.
Love includes not only passion and intimate relationships, but understanding and respect, friendship and accepting. Each of us is unique in his own way and yet we can be two missing pieces of a very beautiful puzzle. I am looking for a reliable man. I need a caring and attentive man who is able to appreciate woman’s beauty, soul and fidelity, the one who will give me the sense of security and who I can love the way he has always dreamed about.
